source.name: FY11_Average Life Insurance Policyholders' Age by State
source.description: The Average Age by State dataset provides the average age of Government life insurance policyholders in the administered programs in each state.  The data is reported at the state level, plus insureds in Military America, Military Europe, Military Pacific, American Samoa, Federated States of Micronesia, Guam, Marshall Islands, Northern Mariana Islands, Puerto Rico, and the Virgin Islands.
